news_header: Brunswick Corp. projects adjusted earnings of $3.50 to $5.00 per share for 2025.
news_original_title: Brunswick Guides FY25 Adj. EPS Below View - Update
news_text: Brunswick Corp. reported its fourth-quarter financial results and provided projections for fiscal 2025, estimating adjusted earnings between $3.50 and $5.00 per share, with net sales expected to range from $5.2 billion to $5.6 billion. Analysts predict earnings of $5.14 per share on net sales of $5.28 billion, excluding special items.
